      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent must confirm correct implementation of governing equations to at least second-order spatial accuracy.",
      "rationale": "MMS study on Navier-Stokes solver confirms second-order spatial convergence (observed order 1.94). Turbulence closure (SST k-omega) verified against canonical channel flow benchmarks. Code verification level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
