      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI on primary QoI (NIH) must be below 10% on the production mesh; three-level refinement study required.",
      "rationale": "Three-level GCI study yields fine-grid GCI of 6.3% on NIH, satisfying the 10% threshold. However, temporal discretization error on transient impeller passage not fully quantified; achieved level capped at 3 rather than required 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted at operating conditions within the COU envelope; fluid properties, hematocrit, and temperature must be documented and matched to CFD boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments conducted at 37°C with bovine blood at 40% hematocrit. Three of five operating points fall within the VAD COU envelope; two extrapolate modestly beyond tested flow rates. Fluid property documentation complete. Achieved level 3; required level 4 not met due to partial envelope coverage."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E% or U_val) must be computed for all QoIs; uncertainty in experimental measurements must be propagated into the comparison.",
      "rationale": "NIH comparison metric computed at all 5 operating points with experimental uncertainty (±5% expanded, k=2). CFD prediction intervals from Monte Carlo UQ bracket all experimental means. One operating point exceeds 30% point-estimate deviation. Achieved level 3; systematic bias at high speed prevents level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
