      "rationale": "NIH is the primary regulatory metric for hemolysis acceptance per FDA guidance. Validation QoI is identical to decision QoI. No transformation required. Achieved level 4 equals required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
