      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must use the same pump geometry, rotational speed range, and fluid analogues as the COU; any geometric or fluid deviations must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used in both validation and COU. Bovine blood analogue accepted as physiologically representative per ASTM F1841. Speed range partially overlapping. Achieved level 3 due to incomplete speed-range coverage in validation dataset."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
