      "rationale": "Continuity and momentum residuals converge to 1e-4; energy and turbulence to 1e-5. Mass imbalance 0.08%. Residual plateau observed in continuity at high-speed operating point; root cause attributed to under-resolved tip clearance vortex. Achieved level 2 below required level 3."
    },
