      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain input parameters must be characterised with probability distributions; Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ must propagate input uncertainty to QoI uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ (n=2000) performed on viscosity, hematocrit, inlet velocity profile, and hemolysis model constants. Surface roughness and tip clearance not included in UQ due to manufacturing data unavailability. Achieved level 3; required level 4 not met due to incomplete input characterisation."
    },
