      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles extracted from upstream PIV planes and applied as CFD inlet BCs. Outlet pressure matched to pump head curve within 2%. Minor swirl component at inlet not captured in CFD BC; sensitivity analysis estimates 3% effect on NIH. Achieved level 3; required level 4 not met due to residual swirl mismatch."
